node.text:
What’s going on is disgusting! But I am so glad we’re fighting back for what we believe in. • 
Color, what is that?! We’re all HUMAN! We all shit the same shit, we all piss the same piss, we all shed the same tears, We all bleed the same, we’re all mothers, fathers , brother, sisters, aunts, uncles ...
• 
Understand this is only the beginning and I will forever stand by your side. And for my Latin community know your roots because we aren’t just made of just one race. So stop being a “pendejo” if you’re racist because that makes no sense. • 
We here baby and we will never fall.
#blacklivesmatter #passtherock

node.text: How those 6 weeks changed me

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Alexis Bianca 🦊 on August 10, 2021 tagging @soultiewaistbeads. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text:
What if all this time, all this struggle, has been leading you to a beautiful chapter in your life? What if everything does work out, even if it doesn’t seem like. It right now? What if who I  became is who I needed all along? What if all this hard work leads to amazing things? What if you replaced negativity with optimism? Would your thoughts and behavior change too?

I believe soo… Dont give up boo!! 
#foxgang

node.text:
Love is not admiring the beauty of the red rose 🌹Love is running your fingers down the sharp thorns and appreciating how something can be so beautiful with all its edges.

No one is perfect and I always thought to be that perfection that never existed. Until I found out my imperfections, my scars , my wounds, my light and darkness is what made me so beautiful..

“Honey, Don’t let anyone take you back from the level you have already leveled up from” Period !! 

Biggest mistake I’ve done in my past and I promise I would never do it again. Been there done that, you’ve learned what happened and sometimes people are just meant to stay as a memory or a lesson. Remember you leveled up for a reason

Stay Foxy my Foxes 🦊
#foxgang
